General.Name: Rodrigo Tekstil Sanayi ve Ticaret AS
General.Description: Rodrigo Tekstil Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. operates clothing and fashion shopping stores in Turkey and internationally. Its products include T-shirts, shirts, sweatshirts, sweater and cardigan, pants, shorts, tracksuits, coats, waistcoats, and jackets. It also offers belts, socks, and perfumes. The company also offers its products online. The company was formerly known as Rodrigo Tekstil Turizm Insaat Gida Ticaret ve Sanayi Anonim Sirketi and changed its name to Rodrigo Tekstil Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. in July 2012. The company was founded in 1993 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey.
